  <original-body>When running rake db:migrate:down VERSION=someversion, them someversion is not removed from the contents of the schema_migrations table. So when rake db:migrate is run, someversion will not be reapplied any more.

The workaround is to manually remove the version from schema_migrations.

Here's a complete moron's guide how to reproduce the problem:
http://dpaste.com/55427/</original-body>
